How long is the course?
It is a SLED approved course. The course is designed to be completed in one day or two evenings.

What is involved in getting a SC CWP permit?
There is a SLED approved course that covers gun safety and handling and concealed carry laws. There is a 50 question written test. You must score a minimum of
70%. You will shoot 50 rounds, 35 of which must be in the black of the silhouette target from 3 to 15 yards.

